==行星系==

在2009年12月中旬，哈佛史密松物理天文台的一組天文學家宣布發現一顆[[系外行星|系外行星]]的伴星，[[GJ_1214_b|GJ 1214 b]]，是一顆有大量的水，和質量與半徑都與地球相近的[[超級地球|超級地球]]<ref name="disco-charbonneau"> {{cite journal |last1=Charbonneau |first1=David |coauthors=Zachory K. Berta, Jonathan Irwin, Christopher J. Burke, Philip Nutzman, Lars A. Buchhave, Christophe Lovis, Xavier Bonfils, David W. Latham, Stéphane Udry, Ruth A. Murray-Clay, Matthew J. Holman, Emilio E. Falco, Joshua N. Winn, Didier Queloz, Francesco Pepe, Michel Mayor, Xavier Delfosse, Thierry Forveille |year=2009 |title=A super-Earth transiting a nearby low-mass star |journal=Nature |volume=462 |issue=17 December 2009 |pages=891–894 |url=http://arxiv1.library.cornell.edu/abs/0912.3229 |doi=10.1038/nature08679 |accessdate=2009-12-15 |pmid=20016595|bibcode = 2009Natur.462..891C }}</ref><ref name="harvardpress">{{cite web |url=http://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2009/pr200924.html |title=Astronomers Find Super-Earth Using Amateur, Off-the-Shelf Technology |author=David A. Aguilar |date=2009-12-16 |work= |publisher=Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics |accessdate=December 16, 2009}}</ref>。

